lead_paragraph: England all-rounder Ben Stokes says he was left devastated by his last over horror show in the World Twenty20 final against West Indies and has yet to watch a re-run of Carlos Brathwaite hitting him for four straight sixes.

headline.print_headline: Devastated Stokes Keen to Move on From Brathwaite Beating
